OL,5, The UK faces making a potentially hefty
OL,6, payment to the EU after its top court  
OL,7, ruled it did too little to prevent     
OL,8, fraud on imports of Chinese clothing.  
OL,10,FEuropean judges said HMRC failed to    
OL,11,Fpass on the correct amount of tax      
OL,12,Frevenue to the EU on imports between   
OL,13,F2011 and 2017.                         
OL,15,FThe European Commission took legal     
OL,16,Faction in 2018, arguing it was owed    
OL,17,F2.7bn euros (#2.4bn).                  
OL,19,FThe UK government said it would respond
OL,20,Fto the judgement "in due course".      
